"samannāgatassa mahāpurisassa dveva gatiyo bhavanti anaññā."
msgstr "And what are the marks which he possesses?"

msgctxt "dn14:55.2"
msgid ""
"Sace agāraṃ ajjhāvasati, rājā hoti cakkavattī dhammiko dhammarājā cāturanto "
"vijitāvī janapadatthāvariyappatto sattaratanasamannāgato."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:55.3"
msgid "Tassimāni sattaratanāni bhavanti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:55.4"
msgid "Seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:55.5"
msgid ""
"cakkaratanaṃ hatthiratanaṃ assaratanaṃ maṇiratanaṃ itthiratanaṃ "
"gahapatiratanaṃ pariṇāyakaratanameva sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:55.6"
msgid ""
"Parosahassaṃ kho panassa puttā bhavanti sūrā vīraṅgarūpā parasenappamaddanā."
msgstr ""

