msgid "‘Eso kho, deva, byādhito nāmā’ti."
msgstr "‘That, sire, is called a sick man.’"

msgctxt "dn14:106.6"
msgid "‘Kiṃ paneso, samma sārathi, byādhito nāmā’ti?"
msgstr "‘But why is he called a sick man?’"

