msgid "‘Tvañca, deva, mayañcamha sabbe byādhidhammā, byādhiṃ anatītā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Everyone is liable to fall sick, sire, including you. No-one is exempt from "
"sickness.’"

msgctxt "dn14:106.10"
msgid ""
"‘Tena hi, samma sārathi, alaṃ dānajja uyyānabhūmiyā, itova antepuraṃ "
"paccaniyyāhī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Well then, my dear charioteer, that’s enough of the park for today. Let’s "
"return to the royal compound.’"

