msgid ""
"‘dhiratthu kira, bho, jāti nāma, yatra hi nāma jātassa jarā paññāyissati, "
"byādhi paññāyissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Damn this thing called birth, since old age and sickness will come to "
"anyone who’s born.’"

